    <section id="id42921055">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id42921062"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis></emphasis>The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id43333548"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Assessment Standard 1.2:</emphasis></emphasis> We know this when the learner describes and illustrates written number systems different to own.</para>
